---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import ContactForm from '../../components/ContactForm.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import RelatedLinks from '../../components/RelatedLinks.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="AromaTouch Body Treatment – Essential Oils | Hingamiskeskus"
  description="AromaTouch body treatment combines doTERRA essential oils with gentle touch techniques. Reduces stress, supports immunity and deep relaxation. Book in Tallinn today!"
  keywords="AromaTouch body treatment"
  lang="en"
  alternates={{ et: '/aromatouch-kehahooldus', ru: '/ru/aromatouch-uhod-za-telom', en: '/en/aromatouch-body-treatment' }}
>

<!-- HEADER -->
<Header active="teenused" lang="en" />

<!-- HERO SECTION (kogu tekst vasakul, pildid paremal) -->
<section class="float-hero">
  <div class="float-hero__content">
    <div class="float-hero__text">
      <h1 class="float-hero__title">AromaTouch body treatment</h1>
      <h2 class="float-hero__subtitle">Therapeutic massage with doTERRA essential oils</h2>
      <p>The AromaTouch technique is a gentle and relaxing body treatment that combines the beneficial properties of doTERRA essential oils with specific touch techniques. This massage-like method was developed by Dr. David Hill, a specialist in the field of essential oils and holistic medicine.</p>
      <h2 class="float-info__heading">Main characteristics and objectives:</h2>
      <p><strong>Gentle touch:</strong> AromaTouch is not a deep massage but rather a light and smooth touch technique focused on relaxing the nervous system and the body.</p>
      <p><strong>Use of essential oils:</strong> A special selection of 8 different doTERRA essential oils or blends is used. These oils are carefully chosen for their therapeutic properties and help balance the body on both a physical and emotional level.</p>
      <p>The effects of the oils can include stress relief, immune system support, anti-inflammatory benefits, relaxation, and mood balancing.</p>
      <p><strong>Body balancing:</strong> The AromaTouch technique is designed to:</p>
      <ul class="float-info__list">
        <li>Reduce stress and anxiety.</li>
        <li>Strengthen the immune system and enhance physical resilience.</li>
        <li>Help the body release inflammation and support natural healing.</li>
        <li>Relax muscles and improve blood circulation.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Working with body points:</strong> The technique focuses on the spine, head, and soles of the feet. The touch technique stimulates the movement of energy within the body and activates the nervous system.</p>
      <p><strong>For the body and mind:</strong> AromaTouch is not just a physical experience but also a way to achieve mental and emotional balance. The combination of essential oils and gentle touch creates a deep sense of relaxation and well-being.</p>
      <p>In summary, the AromaTouch technique is a delicate yet effective way to relax and support the body&#39;s natural healing processes. It is ideal for those looking to improve their well-being through natural and gentle methods. Essential oils reach every cell in the body within 20 seconds, influencing the lymphatic system, tissues, and nervous system while supporting healing at the cellular level. The oils are applied with soft movements to the back and soles of the feet, allowing you to choose which body system you want to support during the session. One thing is certain: afterwards, you will experience deep relaxation and inner peace, enabling your body to begin restoring balance.</p>
      <p><strong>Session duration:</strong> 60 minutes</p>
      <p><strong>Price:</strong> €50</p>
    </div>
    <div class="float-hero__media">
      <img src="/images/aromatouch-naine.jpg" alt="AromaTouch therapist at Hingamiskeskus" class="float-hero__img" loading="lazy" />
      <img src="/images/aromatouch-kuunlad.jpg" alt="AromaTouch treatment room with candles" class="float-hero__img" loading="lazy" style="margin-top: 24px;" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- BOOKING FORM -->
<ContactForm source="Aromatouch kehahooldus (EN)" lang="en" />

<RelatedLinks lang="en" links={[
  { href: "/en/floating", label: "Floating", desc: "Deep relaxation in Epsom salt water" },
  { href: "/en/breathwork", label: "Breathwork", desc: "Guided breathing session in a group" },
  { href: "/en/shop", label: "Shop", desc: "Gift cards and packages" },
]} />

<Footer lang="en" />

</Layout>

<style>
  /* HEADER */
  .header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    background: #fff;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .header__logo img { height: 28px; width: auto; }
  .header__right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .header__cart { color: #1d1e20; }
  .header__burger {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 4px;
  }
  .header__burger span {
    display: block;
    width: 22px;
    height: 2px;
    background: #1d1e20;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .float-hero {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
  }
  .float-hero__content {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-hero__title {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }
  .float-hero__text { text-align: left; }
  .float-hero__title { text-align: left; }
  .float-hero__subtitle { text-align: left; }
  .float-hero__text p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .float-hero__img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  /* INFO / CONTENT */
  .float-info {
    background: #f3fcff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-info p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .float-info p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .float-info__heading {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }
  .float-info__list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .float-info__list li {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }

  /* HERO IMAGE INLINE */
  .float-hero-img {
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  /* SUBTITLE */
  .float-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #1d1e20;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* BOOKING FORM */
  .float-form {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .float-form__title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #1d1e20;
  }
  .float-form__desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .contact-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .contact-form__label {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1d1e20;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  .contact-form__input,
  .contact-form__textarea {
    padding: 12px 14px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #1d1e20;
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }
  .contact-form__input:focus,
  .contact-form__textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: #1f6d85;
  }
  .contact-form__textarea {
    resize: vertical;
  }
  .contact-form__btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #1d1e20;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  /* LOCATION */
  .location {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 20px 24px 24px;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .location__title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .location__address {
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .location__photo {
    width: 80%;
    max-width: 320px;
    margin: 12px auto 0;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 10px;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer__main {
    background: #1f6d85;
    padding: 24px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .footer__logo {
    height: 30px;
    width: auto;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    display: block;
  }
  .footer__contact h3, .footer__hours h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .footer__contact p, .footer__hours p {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .footer__hours {
    margin-top: 16px;
  }
  .footer__social {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .footer__social a { color: #fff; }
  .footer__legal {
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    opacity: 0.7;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    padding-top: 12px;
  }
  .footer__legal a { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; }

  /* DESKTOP */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .header { padding: 12px 40px; }
    .header__logo img { height: 36px; }

    .float-hero { padding: 64px 40px; }
    .float-hero__content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 64px;
      max-width: 1200px;
    }
    .float-hero__text { flex: 1.15; }
    .float-hero__media { flex: 1; position: sticky; top: 100px; }
    .float-hero__title { font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .float-hero__text p { font-size: 16px; }
    .float-info__list li { font-size: 16px; }
    .float-hero__img { margin-top: 0; }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .float-hero__title { font-size: 40px; }
    .float-hero { padding: 56px 40px; }
  }
</style>
